// Unrelated top-level declaration in `com.example`: same simple name `NestedClass`, but NOT a member
// of `SomeClass` and NOT imported by foo.kt. Adding it must not recompile foo.kt once the fix records
// the star-import scope as the class `com.example.SomeClass` rather than the package `com.example`.
class NestedClass
